    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"beautiful noise\" sounds a lot like just performing for no audience. like, if there's no objective meaning, why go through the massive effort of surviving, pain and all, just to make a tiny bit of noise before the void swallows it anyway? it feels more like a trap than a choice.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
